body.description: Finally, travel made trendy with the stylish polyester-twill chevron luggage from Kenneth Cole Reaction’s Chelsea luggage collection. Complete with a fully lined, tear-resistant interior, this luggage also expands an additional 2. 0 inches, ensuring that you have plenty of space for all your needed belongings. Its lightweight construction helps you meet airline weight restrictions to avoid unnecessary airport fees, while its 8-wheel spinners provide effortless 360-degree navigation allowing you to glide quickly through the airport. The main compartment interior features a hanging side zipper pocket and garment restraints to hold belongings in place. The under-the-lid section includes a mesh zipper pocket and a transparent, clear PEVA gusseted pocket for toiletries. The front exterior also features a small zipper pocket for easily accessible items and a large gusseted zipper pocket for additional storage organization. Padded top and side handles allow for easy maneuvering, and a bottom grab handle allows for easier lifting. Additionally, a retractable trolley handle extends to be 41 inches tall with a locking push button mechanism. Fashionable and functional, Chelsea luggage also boasts fashion-forward gold hardware with premium self-repairing coil zippers designed for long-lasting use. Carry-on size meets most U. S. based airline carry-on size requirements and fits into most airline overhead bin compartments. manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: CHELSEA COLLECTION Kenneth Cole Reaction "Chelsea" 8-Wheel Luggage Collection Travel easily with the stylish luggage from Kenneth Cole Reaction’s “Chelsea” collection. Stylish polyester-twill with quilted chevron exterior will be sure to turn heads in the airport. Available in 20”, 24" and 28” tall. Each piece is packed with features including spacious fully lined interiors, garment restraint straps, zipper pockets, and a 2-inch expansion feature in each piece for added carrying capacity. Multi-directional 8-wheel spinners provide smooth 360-degree rotation over rough surfaces allowing you to get where you’re going faster. A traditional, yet stylish suitcase set, perfect for the modern traveler.

Functional Features Retractable Push-Button Handle Sturdy locking retractable push-button telescopic trolley handle conducive for simple, one-handed use.Collapses down in one smooth movement for compact storage when not in use. Multi-Directional 8-Wheel Spinners Allow for smooth movement in any direction, and over any rough surface, for complete mobility free-weight rolling, relieving any pressure from your arms while on the move. Materials Stylish polyester-twill with quilted chevron exterior and fully lined tear-resistant interior.Lightweight construction helps you adhere to airline weight restrictions to avoid unneeded airport fees.

Spacious Compartment Interior Kenneth Cole Brand Kenneth Cole Reaction appeals to fashion-conscious consumers who value both style and function. Each piece reflects a casual urban perspective and a lifestyle uniquely associated with Kenneth Cole. Kenneth Cole Reaction bags feature bold colors, clean lines, and high-quality materials – all of which add up to a casual, yet modern style perfect for both men and women. Kenneth Cole vouches for its uncompromised dedication to providing its customers with a variety of fashion-forward high-quality products with superior workmanship. Whether you are heading to the office or to the airport, when you venture out and travel with a bag from Kenneth Cole, we want you to embark on your journey with confidence and peace of mind. This is why we are keen on even the smallest of details while putting emphasis on fashion, functionality, quality, and durability above all else. Life has a way of coming at us all quickly, so it’s best to be ready for anything, anywhere.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars REALLY nice luggage - VERY happy!
reviews.reviewText: The luggage is exactly as shown - possibly even nicer looking. Super easy to maneuver and the zippers are really heavy weight and durable. Very happy!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars BEST MONEY I HAVE EVER SPENT! BEST LUGGAGE EVER EVER EVER!
reviews.reviewText: I keep telling my friends about it, so I figured it was finally time to make it official! This particular luggage ROCKS and is literally the best "investment" I have ever made. FIVE trips so far and I continue to be so grateful!! Background: I had TAG brand hard shell luggage (hard shell....the new "it" luggage) and this is a night and day difference. Hard shell SO overrated and problematic. This particular KC luggage is pretty, VERY identifiable off the airport luggage belt (black, but puffer design and easy to see gold zippers/extras) and I LOVE it! Super maneuverable and light and pretty w/out being too "pretty" - still very professional and subtle. Also, the zippers are quality! The extra expansion option and outside pockets are AMAZING. Again, even better in person than it looks online. HIGHLY recommend this luggage!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 20, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The wheels do become a bit weak after some time... BUT the quality of the fabric and zipper is super sturdy. I've packed these to the brim a couple of times and it's held up perfectly. They also fit mostly all airplane dimensions to the tee. The number of pockets is perfect. Highly recommend.

reviews.reviewText: Very stylish, easy to move around, carries wieght well but not going to last several years. Two at best.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The design is gorgeous. I can't speak to durability yet because I haven't taken it out traveling very much yet but I presume it's as good as any soft-sided luggage is. The wheels feel pretty solid and smooth.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars This product was inferior
reviews.reviewText: I liked the suitcase so took it on an overseas trip with me. Once filled (14 lbs and less) it did not track straight and was wavy. The handle waswas not sturdy, wabbly, would not always stay locked in. In Vietnam it went in front of me slightly but enough to cause me to fall onto my head requiring 3 stitches. Unfortunately the return date on Amazon was five days before I returned. I would like to return and get a refund.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great compact briefcase
reviews.reviewText: It came early which was great. It was well packed and professional wrapped. It was in mint condition. She had plastic on it from the warehouse. Very roomie, but small just for pushing it with you on your travels where it would be office or work. This is a great size for under seat plane ride and great over nighter. I will buy this again, and my friend just got her on to use in the office, for files and organizing her daily assignments. And for schooling with heavy books great for everyday life duties.

reviews.reviewTitle: Nice quality, rolling bag is a bit small for my 17" laptop
reviews.reviewText: It's very nice. Handle feels a bit wobbly, but it's fine. It's nice looking. I love the liner colours because they aren't black, which I find difficult to see into. Price is a bit high at times. I'd buy again at the price I paid even if it was a bit high.

Unfortunately, as much as I liked how this product looked, it turned out to not even hold out fir one trip. The top handle is flimsy and I had to fix it quite a few times and put it back in place. The tag broke off and it is completely unreliable without a handle to rol it around with. I have to return it as it is too much money not to and I am terribly disappointed. So inconvenient.
